**WORKFLOW 0 — Understand Project**: Familiarize with the Raycast UI clone project. Tech stack: Bun, TypeScript strict, React 19, Vite 6, Sass. File naming convention: snake_case. No comments unless JSDoc for public API.

**WORKFLOW 1 — Read progress.txt**: Find the most important pending task. Priority is determined by `[P<number>]` tags. `[P0]` = do first. `[P>999]` = low priority, do when possible but never ignore. If a low-priority task takes too long and higher-priority tasks exist, document progress and revert status.

**WORKFLOW 2 — No pending tasks**: If all tasks are done, plan next improvements, add tasks, and stop.

**WORKFLOW 3 — Execute tasks**: Sequential pipeline: evaluate scope (break into sub-tasks if >3 files) → execute → `bun run check` → launch review agent → review & correct → update progress.txt → commit → output status → stop.

